# Circuit Wiring Diagrams

**Basic Components Required**
- 1x NodeMCU ESP32 Development board
- 1x LED (To show running status)
- 1x Quectel EG25-G LTE Modem
- 1x HW-125 Micro SD Card Module
    - Requires SD card with $\geq$ __MB of storage

**Basic Diagram**


### **1)** DC Power Source
**Additional Components Required**
- 1x 5V output DC Power Module
    - I have tested with the Elegoo ARD-POWERMOD

### **2)** USB Battery Pack Power Source

### **3)** Custom Power Source
You are free to use your own power source for the project, just ensure you are only feeding a maximum of 5V into your components so you don't fry anything. \
\
Also, be sure you can power off or disconnect your power source before flashing the program code onto your board, or you may run into issues with some boards.